# large per-run forensic LLM-trace dumps (re-derivable by re-running; the committed *_findings.md +
# summary JSON + stdout are the verifiable record). Full traces contain every prompt/reply and are big.
experiments/results/exp104_simulate_world_traces.json
experiments/results/exp104_checkpoints/
experiments/results/exp104_checkpoints_*/

# large re-derivable data-scaling caches (rebuild: python -m experiments.data.build_scaling_caches)
